io.oasp.module.basic.common.api.to

Class AbstractCto

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.oasp.module.basic.common.api.to.AbstractTo
      • io.oasp.module.basic.common.api.to.AbstractCto
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, net.sf.mmm.util.entity.api.Entity, net.sf.mmm.util.transferobject.api.TransferObject

    public abstract class AbstractCto
extends AbstractTo
    This is the abstract base class for a composite transfer-object. Such object should contain (aggregate) other AbstractTransferObjects but no atomic data. This means it has properties that contain a TransferObject or a Collection of those but no values.
    Classes extending this class should carry the suffix Cto.

    hohwille
